trans-unit.source: Determines the shapes of connector points on a workflow design surface.
trans-unit.target: Determina as formas de pontos de conector uma superfície de desenho de fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] Connectors are the lines rendered on the workflow design surface between interconnected activity designers.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]Os conectores são as linhas compostas na superfície de desenho de fluxo de trabalho entre os estruturadores de atividades interligado.

trans-unit.source: The ends of each line are called connector points, which are where the lines attach to the activity designers that they connect.
trans-unit.target: As extremidades de cada linha são denominadas conector pontos, em que as linhas anexar os estruturadores de atividades que se ligam.

trans-unit.source: LineAnchor provides values that determine the appearance of the connector points.
trans-unit.target: LineAnchor fornece valores que determinam o aspeto dos pontos de conector.
